# Routin. — RESTful API Specification

## Conventions

- **Base URL:** `https://api.routin.app/v1`
- **Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer <access_token>` (JWT)
- **Response envelope:**

```json
// Success
{ "success": true,  "data": {},    "message": "" }
// Error
{ "success": false, "error": { "code": "ERR_CODE", "message": "" } }
```

- **Roles:** `Admin` | `User` (Premium/Free)
- `[A]` = Admin only · `[U]` = User (auth) · `[*]` = cả hai · `[-]` = Public
- **Status:** ✅ DONE · 🔨 IN PROGRESS · ⏳ PENDING
- **FE Contract Doc:** `docs/FE_API_REQUEST_RESPONSE.md`

