### 6.2 Pending

| Method | Endpoint                    | Access | Mô tả                                        |
| ------ | --------------------------- | ------ | -------------------------------------------- |
| POST   | `/payments/callback/vnpay`  | [-]    | Webhook VNPay                                |
| POST   | `/payments/callback/momo`   | [-]    | Webhook MoMo                                 |
| POST   | `/payments/verify`          | [A]    | Admin xác nhận chuyển khoản thủ công         |

**Flow: Đăng ký Premium**

```
1. GET  /subscription-plans              → user chọn gói
2. POST /subscriptions { planId }
          → tạo UserSubscription (Pending)
          → tạo Transaction (Pending)
          → trả về { payment_url }
3. User redirect → PayOS checkout
4. POST /subscriptions/webhook/payos      → PayOS callback
          → cập nhật Transaction → Success
          → cập nhật UserSubscription → Active
          → mở khóa Premium features (Reels upload, AI suggestions)
```

**Premium Features unlock:**

- Upload ảnh/video check-in (evidence)
- AI routine suggestions
- Detailed analytics & streak history
- Unlimited public routines

