### 7.1 Follow & Block — API Plan (Code next)

| Method | Endpoint               | Access | Mô tả                                      | Status |
| ------ | ---------------------- | ------ | ------------------------------------------ | ------ |
| POST   | `/users/:id/follow`    | [*]    | Follow user                                 | ✅     |
| DELETE | `/users/:id/follow`    | [*]    | Unfollow user                               | ✅     |
| GET    | `/users/:id/followers` | [-]    | Danh sách followers                         | ✅     |
| GET    | `/users/:id/following` | [-]    | Danh sách following                         | ✅     |
| POST   | `/users/:id/block`     | [*]    | Block user (auto-unfollow hai chiều)        | ✅     |
| DELETE | `/users/:id/block`     | [*]    | Unblock user                                | ✅     |
| GET    | `/users/me/blocks`     | [*]    | Danh sách user đã block                     | ✅     |

**Flow: Follow/Block rules**

```
POST /users/:id/follow
  → reject nếu self-follow
  → reject nếu có block 1 trong 2 chiều
  → idempotent nếu đã follow

POST /users/:id/block
  → insert UserBlocks
  → remove Follow (me->target, target->me) nếu có
  → (phase chat) remove direct conversation access khi cần
```

